{"data":[{"id":562320273,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5e001cb5d9d4fba7760a18275ec70fe5","url_token":"sysback-11","name":"sysback","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5e001cb5d9d4fba7760a18275ec70fe5","user_type":"people","headline":"学学学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":3,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562320273","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546074210,"updated_time":1546074210,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e在国内哥德巴赫猜想的热度不逊色于庞加莱猜想。一个籍籍无名的俄罗斯数学家格里戈里·佩雷尔曼解决了庞加莱猜想，获得了巨大的名誉，纽约州立大学石溪分校曾希望聘请他为教授，他可以提任何条件随便什么样的薪水，甚至一年只在学校出现一个月都可以。然而你觉得证明了哥德巴赫猜只能保送清北数学系？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个问题实在是太低估这些知名数学猜想的难度，又太高估进入清北的难度了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你这个问题就好像在问：如果我成为了亿万富翁，能买得起一包卫龙辣条么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“当一切都看起来无济于事的时候，我去看一个石匠敲石头。他一连敲了100次，石头仍然纹丝不动。但当他敲第101次的时候，石头裂为两半。可我知道，让石头裂开的不是那最后一击，而是前面的一百次敲击的结果。”——雅各布·里斯\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"When nothing seems to help,I go and look at a stonecutter hammering away at his rock perhaps a hundred times without as much as a crack showing in it.Yet at the hundred and first blowit will split in two,and I know it was not that blow that did it——but all that had gone before.\"——Jacob Riis\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我有些时候也总是觉得世界上是有敲门砖这种东西的，也幻想过我要拿到怎么的敲门砖就可以自由生活了。这真是一种天真的想法。世界创造了这样一种幻觉，只需要随随便便找一找捡一捡就可以了，忽视了真正的过程。如果真的脚踏实地的走到最后，会发现不是结果决定了什么，而是过程决定了结果，而在这个过程中，你早已不是原来的自己了。。。世界赞赏了不是那块裂成两块的破石头，而是他妈的学会了砸石头的你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是有个高中生证明了哥猜，你说他会是啥样的，自学数学专著数百本，每天工作12小时，草纸打了几十万张，著有相关论文数千页。好吧，你能做到这点，就算没证明了，大学随便挑。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"在国内哥德巴赫猜想的热度不逊色于庞加莱猜想。一个籍籍无名的俄罗斯数学家格里戈里·佩雷尔曼解决了庞加莱猜想，获得了巨大的名誉，纽约州立大学石溪分校曾希望聘请他为教授，他可以提任何条件随便什么样的薪水，甚至一年只在学校出现一个月都可以。然而你…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1198\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_commen